{"tid":27933,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每日都好似行屍酒肉","createTime":"2016-12-07T15:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T17:26:38.000Z","uid":19369,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32aaee3e713931905388b336ce3b13c0336c60df","tid":27933,"uid":19369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:35:13.000Z","msg":"今年三十歲，讀書唔叻，死讀爛讀再靠埋10 9 政府資助，捱到非3大大學畢業，已經26歲，做左四年野，而家先搵得果24、5k..公屋仔，屋企人無乜讀過書，做既都係保安同搬搬抬抬....<br />\n<br />\n上年阿爸cancer，十鳩公立醫生唔肯醫，私家醫生做手術要一球野去醫，無保險無積蓄乜7都無，最後又投訴又呢又路搞左幾個月都無結果，到最後腦幹死，生又唔係死又唔係，隔多兩個零禮拜真係唔忍心就叫醫生停藥放佢走...走左一年...到而家為止成日都係度諗究竟果陣自己有無盡力去救佢，講緊一球野，如果要救去借大耳窿又好乜7都好，但係就無做到...每次諗番起都覺得自己好軟弱..唔敢承擔起呢個責任，唔夠膽咩條數...而屋企人唔知話佢地唔識思考定on99,d死人醫生講咩就信咩，乜7都旨意晒你去做你去決定....你唔講佢地就哦哦哦，你講佢地又係哦哦哦，你話事啦....我頂！<br />\n<br />\n呢一年入面每隔一排就會諗番起當時既情境....有時收工係條街度好似on99咁行屍酒肉，做人好似無晒目標唔知想點咁，過得一日得一日，有時會諗咁撚辛苦做乜鳩，死左乜7都帶唔走....睇番自己身邊既朋友環境各樣都好好，讀書唔成唔緊要，屋企有錢，俾你去外國讀書，讀完書番黎做份10 9 工搵果雞碎咁少都唔緊要，俾間公司你跟著做老闆，結婚俾埋錢你結，又車又樓送埋俾你！最撚好笑係佢仲問你幾時結婚！我屌你老母你估我係你咩有父幹！我老豆一早死撚左啦！<br />\n<br />\n成日都安慰自己，其實呢d咁既故事香港周撚圍慘過你幾百倍都仲有。但係呢幾個月經常性見到fb都係求婚結婚生仔既情況，個人就更加惆悵，到底無父幹點樣先可以成功！？屌你老味樓價咁高，公屋居屋又無你份，就算供得起又點，首期都俾唔撚起....<br />\n<br />\n唉，sorry 呢個post其實無咩主題...只係夜欄人靜...心差又差...想發洩下撩下人吹水....<br />\n<br />\n有無人有咩經歷互相share下鼓勵下..."},{"pid":"8eb4911906447c97ed7ce25708ac51ae1815914f","tid":27933,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想自己一個去旅行散下心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225ede811055db0541e5e272194bfaa6faf7183e","tid":27933,"uid":7957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:39:48.000Z","msg":"雖然我仲未去到你呢個年紀<br />\n但過多幾年 讀埋書就要出黎捱<br />\n見到你既經歷 我好似望見我既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db7039d4bb54161399a0da3242632a5299a2883","tid":27933,"uid":15482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978500fe530a7f2218d64145085919cfd936a6b6","tid":27933,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"好多人都差唔多"},{"pid":"020841784da81f9ab346656c1d0d5d91bb30a525","tid":27933,"uid":41743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"加油啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1940971118e9f3bf59349ca7630744117808954f","tid":27933,"uid":19369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:50:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想自己一個去旅行散下心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年中自己都去左一轉，仲好健康去旅行都跑步....果陣好似好relax...但之後又回到現實...<br />\n有時覺得好似一個惡性循環咁...突然又浮出黎....跟著就好似以前中化既文章咁思考人生的意義...屌你老母發覺基本搵唔到個意義....唉..."},{"pid":"320d2b6cf410a6064a4f8eacaf66c5e4d90ce717","tid":27933,"uid":19369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然我仲未去到你呢個年紀<br />\n但過多幾年 讀埋書就要出黎捱<br />\n見到你既經歷 我好似望見我既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出黎捱唔緊要...讀好書出黎都可以差好遠架啦...抽d時間陪屋企人唔好掛住拍拖去玩...得閒同老豆老母飲下茶...父親節果d記住買個蛋糕...<br />\n唉以前總係覺得永遠仲有下次仲有時間....人大啦...時間去得好快，好多野唔係自己控制得到..."},{"pid":"6b3d8ea117c5579e1e7ff245010bd1bf42541c53","tid":27933,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92cca0b1144a784ea3292e30f51e373fffe9e1e","tid":27933,"uid":47515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:55:24.000Z","msg":"巴打加油"},{"pid":"3d493ebd11882556dbaacb03a05052559e75d46e","tid":27933,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 撐落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdfb901cff3ad3e308a2f0b81c33578be0b86e1a","tid":27933,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打加油"},{"pid":"18560801312ed4af7202386816cd16cd7f437c43","tid":27933,"uid":3514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:40:15.000Z","msg":"巴打加油，身邊總有家人、朋友支持你"},{"pid":"39f47b681865da319672321a54d48101942bb19c","tid":27933,"uid":50327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"際遇總會有改變既一日，巴打要加油<br />\n我都係過來人"},{"pid":"edae62e5a6af5e157d907e24678d3bae1e999856","tid":27933,"uid":31238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>雖然我仲未去到你呢個年紀<br />\n但過多幾年 讀埋書就要出黎捱<br />\n見到你既經歷 我好似望見我既將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n出黎捱唔緊要...讀好書出黎都可以差好遠架啦...抽d時間陪屋企人唔好掛住拍拖去玩...得閒同老豆老母飲下茶...父親節果d記住買個蛋糕...<br />\n唉以前總係覺得永遠仲有下次仲有時間....人大啦...時間去得好快，好多野唔係自己控制得到...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝巴打提醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有時我都搵唔到人生意義..."},{"pid":"7d82e36e92a0d33cd4e4a262694ba58f28880e1f","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:59:41.000Z","msg":"樓主加油"},{"pid":"641c9dfc6f056b97f2ebc2fdff8d518f61432a32","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:59:53.000Z","msg":"加油！！！"},{"pid":"02681e30899a0c80ef8021130b50defe7f459fc2","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:00:15.000Z","msg":"加油呀！！！"},{"pid":"f32a0ca4884feb6083e1640ba2527128269d1f38","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"你得嫁！！！"},{"pid":"7b886aa185c95d60b2f9becf50c99104bd252f1b","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"844d71fbfcd6bb3c3d7d292ab5317bf61c953cb7","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:01:38.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"66181fccacba928dd9394ac01d24478e5472ab1f","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"a43b5c6e2059d441da584096a6c7220ed981a2db","tid":27933,"uid":13802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:01:59.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"ffe37734e32e47cbc5f0cc8b2a56a70a75ccc7dd","tid":27933,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de168cc16d52e2a7ed03a10de027e59dade8a21a","tid":27933,"uid":15441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:11:41.000Z","msg":"加油！有啲經歷同你好似，又係屋企人有事，每日行屍走肉，每一日都好似唔知為乜而生存，同朋友講佢地都好似唔會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到屋企人走左又諗返起，佢無事行得走得果陣，我有無做好自己？有無好好孝順佢？有無比佢享過福？有事果陣見到佢咁又幫佢唔到，分擔唔到，果種痛又有無人會明？<br />\nSorry,係到留底左負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要加油呀！希望捱到盡頭便是陽光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋去旅行散心都無用既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返到黎好似比未去時更灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}